room_title: Escape room "Treasure Island" by ALL IN Adventures in Tuscaloosa
room_address: 1800 Mcfarland Blvd. E, Suite 302 Tuscaloosa, AL 35404
room_description:
Ye’ve been shipwrecked on an island with signs of Pirates everywhere! You and yer mateys need to solve the mystery and escape the island before they return. Or it’s off with yer heads!
Also available in an easier difficulty level (1).
